body:
I made my one year as an avicus Senior Moderator on September 13th, 2015. My one year as mapdev is in a few hours and I've been serving the staff team and event staff team for over a year now. I've been part of this amazing community for many years now (since I was 12) and now I'm 15 and In a while 16. Anyways ask me anything. If you are wondering why it is an "AMAA" is because some people always have questions some people don't want to answer or they just ask a stupid question. So yea...

❤️ @jozz & @mango
